<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_44_r1l11">Lıeber her Peter / Vns hat <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> lıeber <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l14"> <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendell / Als vvir den 
