<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l34"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>linhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>lebenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
