</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_44" id="21v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Peter von Spawr </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Peter, uns hat <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber
                                <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell
                            <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendell als wir den <add>vormals</add>
                        czu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Osterreich gnaden gesant heten von der hab und
                                <expan>kauffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wegen, als her
                                <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Flednicz und her
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Weispriach, sein diener, den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>hersch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan> auf<expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und etlich die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey
                            <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wol gesagt und czu wissen getan, wie ir im
                        darynne gen <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> gar <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und beholffen gewesen seit, des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                                <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>; und also
                            <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>darümb</add> czu <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und
                        auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> von Osterreich
                                    <add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und diener Hansen
                            <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Prager mit iren <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> davon czureden.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in gen der
                                <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Osterreich
                                <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> ewr günstige hilff und
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> aber
                            <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweisen wollet durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Martini.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Graf <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vom
                            <expan>Heiligenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>, <lb/>graf
                                <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Meͣtsch, <lb/>graf
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Metsch,
                            <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Linhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Lebenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Casparn von Slandersperg, <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Freuntsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                        <lb/>Nyclasen Vintler <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
